{"tid":2193760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普及檢測會交叉感染　衞生防護中心呼籲有病徵市民不應參與","createTime":"2020-09-08T05:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T06:47:57.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e349eea8127b35391cbfb6802a45f77db071147c","tid":2193760,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200906184443/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=404555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200906184443%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404555&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=cb57dc17\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200906184443/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=404555</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心再次呼籲，有病徵市民不應該參與計劃，避免交叉感染。<br />\n<br />\n本港單日確診再度回升至雙位數，最新確診21宗個案，其中五宗在普及社區檢測發現。<br />\n<br />\n一對年長夫婦及外傭同住尖沙咀港景峯，三人在上星期三去做全民檢測確診。他們在上月底先後出現喉嚨痛、咳嗽等病徵，本月曾多次去青山道馮建華私家醫生求診，斷診兩夫婦有肺炎，但未有進行檢測。這名醫生、六名護士及一名清潔工被列為密切接觸者，需要送去檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心再次呼籲，有病徵的市民不適宜參與普及社區檢測。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君：「當然希望市民有病徵就去看醫生和領取樣本瓶，或以其他途徑測試，盡量不要等待全民檢測有位置再測試，有時可能會阻慢了病情，要預約到時間才能進行，希望是沒有病徵的市民去進行檢疫中心，減低交叉傳播的風險。」"},{"pid":"58023c40db8b26407781e2dc19c69de7f5bace02","tid":2193760,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"搞個垃圾檢測之前就應該呼籲啦<br />\n高估藍屍智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39842a1808f301bb0e96f68151fa1c558611712","tid":2193760,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"2a4ab738e8cbd537dddfb8072a013f0b2c7ca1bc","tid":2193760,"uid":237517,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"有病徵唔比去<br />\n<br />\n無病先比去<br />\n<br />\n咁搞黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d3e538e070e846bc525bef2e2e07c3d04461ce","tid":2193760,"uid":35946,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"政府：而家係俾大家驗下自己有無病，但有病嘅唔好嚟驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑唔笑死人，不如執柒咗佢算吧"},{"pid":"2abfd24149b482c193e1c69d5b00eb7c5d81ce45","tid":2193760,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"無病徵但有事 我鬼知咩"},{"pid":"cd4be8d0d773f4fb5f2b0d104dde463e0a0fad1f","tid":2193760,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a4ab738e8cbd537dddfb8072a013f0b2c7ca1bc","tid":2193760,"uid":237517,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"有病徵唔比去<br />\n<br />\n無病先比去<br />\n<br />\n咁搞黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0b9a14a7479502e429b6545cc02c4e58cf1728","tid":2193760,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"而家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c5abd430c1c732a435c72cd9d8dc2cebae1e15","tid":2193760,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又嚟team kill"},{"pid":"129890681bd5b2c464c0cb95a6ca574816e7770b","tid":2193760,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"你班仆街自己出去驗完make sure無事先好嚟驗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076e548159c7dc99681d0ee70629f29947290a8f","tid":2193760,"uid":295602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"病徵又唔係非常獨特<br />\n本身又可以冇病徵<br />\n屌, 一般市民撚識分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家都未有檢測群組已經偷笑"}]}